"3 cups unsalted chicken stock (such as Swanson)","1 cup water","2 tablespoons plus 2 tsp. extra-virgin olive oil, divided","1/2 teaspoon salt","8 ounces uncooked whole-grain rotini pasta","2 1/2 ounces Parmesan cheese, grated (about 2/3 cup), divided","1  large yellow squash, halved lengthwise and sliced (about 1 1/2 cups)","1 cup chopped tomato","1  medium zucchini, grated on the large holes of a box grater (about 1 cup)","2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","1/4 cup torn fresh basil leaves"